<div type="edition" xml:lang="san-Latn" rendition="class:83225 maturity:83211"><!--
Comments below by Csaba Kiss are offered "as is" and do not represent a thoroughly researched or considered opinion.
--><p><lb
n="1"/>Oṁ svasti mānagr̥hāc chruta-naya-vinaya-śauryya-dhairyya-vīryyādy-aśeṣa-
<lb
n="2"/>sad-guṇa-gaṇādhāro liccavi-kula-ketur bhaṭṭāraka-mahārāja-śrī-śi<lb
n="3" break="no"/>vadevaḥ kuśalī Āṅlābakasapitā-narasiṁhobhaya-pāñcālī<!--
L3.  1 Bh.I. has kuśalī - - - - pitā narasimho bhaya - - - -
--><lb
n="4"/>nivāsino yathāpradhānaṅ grāma-kuṭumbinaḥ kuśalam ābhāṣya
<lb
n="5"/>samājñāpayati viditam bhavatu bhavatāṁ yathānena pr̥thu-sa<lb
n="6" break="no"/>mara-sampāta-nirjayādhigata-śauryya-pratāpopahata-saka<!--
L6.  2 Bh.I.: °pratāpāpahata°
--><lb
n="7" break="no"/>la-śatru-pakṣa-prabhāvena samyak-prajā-pālana-pariśramopārjji<lb
n="8" break="no"/>ta-śubhra-yaśobhivyāpta-diṅmaṇḍalena śrīmahāsā<add place="below">ma</add>ntāmśuvarmma<lb
n="9" break="no"/>ṇā yuṣmad-dhita-vidhānāya vijñāpitena mayaitad-gauravā<lb
n="10" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->d yuṣmad-anukampa</supplied>yā ca kūther-vr̥tty-adhikr̥tānāṁ samucita<!--
L10. In this line Bh.I. reads nyadhikr̥tānā samucita - - only
--><lb
n="11" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->s tri-kara-mātra-sādhanāyaiva praveśo lekhya-dāna</supplied>
<lb
n="12"/>pañcāparādhādy-arthan tv apraveśa Iti prasādo vaḥ kr̥<lb
n="13" break="no"/>tas tad evaṁ-vedibhir asmac-caraṇa-talopajīvibhir anyair vā
<lb
n="14"/>na kaiścid ayam prasādo <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>nyathā karaṇīyo yas tv etām ājñāṁ vilaṅghyā<lb
n="15" break="no"/>nyathā kuryyāt kārayed vā tam aham atitarā<supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->n na</supplied> marṣayiṣyā<lb
n="16" break="no"/>mi bhāvibhir api bhūpatibhir dharmma-gurubhir gguru-kr̥ta-prasā<lb
n="17" break="no"/>dānuvarttibhir iyam ājñā samyak pratipālanīyā dūtakaś cātra
<lb
n="18"/>vipravarmmagomī saṁvaT <num value="518"><g type="numeral">500</g> <g type="numeral">10</g> 8</num> prathamāṣāḍha-śukla-dvādaśyāM||
</p>
